suggestions.name: Hike Table Mountain
suggestions.description: We will get to hike one of the New 7 Wonders of Nature to see a great view of Cape Town.

suggestions.name: Great White Shark Cage Dive
suggestions.description: We will get to go to Gaansbai to dive with Great White Sharks to see them upclose!

suggestions.name: Snorkel with Seals
suggestions.description: We get to snorkel with hundreds of seals of Cape Town's coast!

suggestions.name: Sand Boarding
suggestions.description: It is like snowboarding... but on a sand dune!

suggestions.name: Meet lots of dog friends
suggestions.description: Make friends and play with them

suggestions.name: Visit Stellenbosch Vineyards
suggestions.description: Some of the top wine in the world comes from this region! Let's bring a picnic and go wine tasting.

suggestions.name: Sunrise at Lion's Head Mountain
suggestions.description: We can have a 360 degree view of Cape Town while the sunrises over it!

suggestions.name: Cliff Jump in Santorini
suggestions.description: Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants did it... and so should we!

suggestions.name: Eat ALL the Amazing Seafood
suggestions.description: The Cave of Nikolas restaurant in Santorini has amazing, fresh seafood.

suggestions.name: Visit Animal Kingdom
suggestions.description: We can go on the Everest Ride and see lots of animals!

suggestions.name: Watch Sunset from Oia
suggestions.description: The Sun sets around 8pm when we're there!

suggestions.name: Visit Wineries
suggestions.description: The wineries have tastings and charcuterie boards for us!

suggestions.name: Ride ATVs
suggestions.description: We can rent ATVs and ride them to the beaches across the island.
